Package: DeCAFS
Type: Package
Title: Detecting Abrupt Changes in the Presence of Local Fluctuations and Autocorrelated Noise
Version: 3.1.2
Date: 2020-04-22
Author: Gaetano Romano, Guillem Rigaill, Vincent Runge, Paul Fearnhead
Maintainer: Gaetano Romano <g.romano@lancaster.ac.uk>
Description: An algorithm to detect abrupt changes in time series with local fluctuations as a random walk process and auto-correlated noise via an AR(1) process.
